{"tid":189761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"深圳市教育局微信公布　港澳籍學生可申請參加積分入學","createTime":"2017-04-06T16:07:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-07T04:02:48.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5c840596b53ce80dc6f8128c696e04eef5bec7ab","tid":189761,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T16:07:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1323796_1_L_20170406233754.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1323796_1_L_20170406233754.jpg&h=afa2a40f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n深圳市教育局公布，港澳籍學生可以申請參加積分入學。（港台圖片）<br />\n深圳市教育局官方微信公布，港澳籍學生可以申請參加積分入學。<br />\n<br />\n深圳市教育局近日發布下學年學校招生通知，市內各區將於4月中旬開始接受網上申請，其中市內義務教育招生政策更新，包括港澳籍學生，可以與非深圳戶籍學生一樣，申請參加積分入學，以及取消將符合計劃生育政策作為申請入學的必備條件，將計劃生育作為積分入學專案等。<br />\n<br />\n以往居於深圳而又擁有香港居留權的學生，由於沒有內地戶籍，未能享受內地免費義務教育，須到香港跨區上學。<br />\n<br />\n教育界立法會議員葉建源歡迎深圳放寬入學限制，認為可以紓緩學額不足的壓力，但由於深圳的公布未有細則，包括收生標準，以及學額數量，未知最終效果。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1323796-20170406.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1323796-20170406.htm&d=JcMWRxryG4qpJesfomKpWL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=a1dfb8e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1323796-20170406.htm&h=c933ab2a\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1323796-20170406.htm</a>"},{"pid":"6d25f9d937f9f500771614157deb8feb7411e45a","tid":189761,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T16:13:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"be2c05f3a63b4e4246d57de703526d8fbb6c6754","tid":189761,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T17:58:13.000Z","msg":"長期離港取消港籍？"},{"pid":"2d2d2b6cd19423400692b404fe4bf1074cfe60af","tid":189761,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T17:59:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>